George Dewhurst (director) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Dewhurst_(director) 0 George Dewhurst (1889 in Preston, Lancashire, England - 8 November 1968 in Tooting, London, England) was a British actor, screenwriter and film director. He directed several film versions of the play A Sister to Assist 'Er.
